# DaKanji-DB-Core sources

## `./conversion/`

Conversion of data sources that ARE NOT native yomitan dictionaries to DaKanji DB format.
This includes conversion to DaKanji directly, or first to a DaKanji DB supported format.

## `./database`

Contains everything that defines the database, ie.: views tables etc.

## `./parsing`

Parsing of data sources that ARE native yomitan dictionaries
